PrecisAppointment of QUSSAI SAMAK, of Laval, Quebec, MARIE-CLAIRE HÉLIE, of Outremont, Quebec, and EDWIN CHARLES AQUILINA, of Ottawa, Ontario, as members of the National Round Table on the Environment and the Economy, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
